data.title: Fingertec – Fingerprint TimeLine 100
data.text:
Description

FingerTec Fingerprint

Model: TimeLine 100

SPECIFICATIONS

Model : TimeLine 100

Surface Finishing : Acrylonitrile butadiene styrene (ABS)

Type Of Antenna : RFID

Microprocessor : 400 MHz

Memory : 8 MB flash memory & 32 MB SDRAM

Algorithm : BioBridge VX 9.0

Push Technology : Yes

Product Dimension (L X W X H) mm : 190 x 50 x 140

Fingerprint templates : 10000

Transaction : 30000

ENROLLMENT & VERIFICATION

Methods : Card & password

Card per user ID : 1

Reading distance, mm : 40 ~ 80 (RFID, HID), 30 ~ 50 (Mifare)

Verification time (sec) : < 1

CARD TECHNOLOGY

RFID: 64-bit, 125kHz

MIFARE: MFIS50/S70, 13.56MHz

HID: HID 1325, 26-bit, 125kHz

COMMUNICATIONS

Method : TCP/IP, USB disk (Optional: RS232 & RS485)

Baud rates : 9600, 19200, 38400, 57600, 115200

OPERATING ENVIRONMENT

Temperature (°C) : 0 ~ 45

Humidity (%) : 20 ~ 80

Power input : DC 5V 2A

TIME ATTENDANCE

Siren : Built in and external

Word codes : Yes

MULTIMEDIA

Voice : Yes

Display : Black & White

Short Messaging : Yes

VOICE / DISPLAY LANGUAGE (TERMINAL)

English (Standard), Arabic, Indonesian, Chinese (Simplified), Cantonese /

Chinese (Traditional), Thai, Vietnamese, Spanish, Portuguese (Portugal),

French, Russian, German, Turkish & Persian

Other languages are available upon request.
